" <M-h> will disable hlsearch.
" Unfortunately, ViEmu is buggy and won't redraw highlightings when hlsearch
" is re-enabled by :set invhlsearch, so this can't be a toggle binding. :(
imap <M-h> <C-O><M-h>
map <M-h> :noh<CR>

" <C-Down> will jump to the current tag (<C-]> is too hard on German keyboards).
imap <C-Down> <C-O><C-Down>
map <C-Down> <C-]>

" <C-Up> will jump back again.
imap <C-Up> <C-O><C-Up>
map <C-Up> <C-T>
